This task was given during the on going HNG intenship to add a new feature of interest calculator into Piggyvest plateform.
Out team made up of frontend and backend decided to work on the investment page. We undertand that not all user can easily calculate how much 
yield their money will bring at the end of a certain period. We decided to integegrate calculator in each field of investement opportunity.

Technology Used:
The frontend was HTML, CSS and Boostrap While the  back was ASP.Net MVC

What we achieved:
We were able to make it possible for a user to quickly know how much he or she is expecting if he invest.
We were able to loop out calclulator at every investment filed.
The calculator could pick the rate, period, while the user input the amout and get his interest.

